become even more familiar and to

00:24:07.436 --> 00:24:08.726 A:middle
be able to support this in your

00:24:08.726 --> 00:24:09.000 A:middle
apps.

00:24:11.356 --> 00:24:12.316 A:middle
Additionally, if you have

00:24:12.316 --> 00:24:13.926 A:middle
image-based apps, we need to

00:24:13.926 --> 00:24:15.786 A:middle
allow image descriptions to be

00:24:15.786 --> 00:24:17.586 A:middle
added at share time by the

00:24:17.586 --> 00:24:19.646 A:middle
poster so that VoiceOver can

00:24:19.646 --> 00:24:21.556 A:middle
have something personalized to

00:24:21.556 --> 00:24:23.026 A:middle
describe the photo with.

00:24:23.546 --> 00:24:25.406 A:middle
Otherwise, new in VoiceOver this

00:24:25.406 --> 00:24:27.586 A:middle
year is image analysis to

00:24:27.586 --> 00:24:29.056 A:middle
describe the image contents or

00:24:29.056 --> 00:24:30.626 A:middle
composition, or if type is

00:24:30.626 --> 00:24:31.836 A:middle
overlaid on images.

00:24:32.316 --> 00:24:35.136 A:middle
But a handcrafted description

00:24:35.136 --> 00:24:36.296 A:middle
will always be preferred.

00:24:37.016 --> 00:24:38.736 A:middle
Twitter has done a great job at

00:24:38.736 --> 00:24:40.406 A:middle
adding image description options

00:24:40.406 --> 00:24:41.376 A:middle
to their Tweet sheets.

00:24:42.676 --> 00:24:45.156 A:middle
So, another area that reduces

00:24:45.156 --> 00:24:47.996 A:middle
hurdles and barriers for apps is

00:24:48.366 --> 00:24:49.846 A:middle
integrating with Siri.

00:24:50.046 --> 00:24:51.886 A:middle
Siri is the ultimate quick

00:24:51.886 --> 00:24:54.466 A:middle
access to your app that doesn't

00:24:54.466 --> 00:24:56.806 A:middle
even require looking or holding,

00:24:56.806 --> 00:24:58.106 A:middle
or touching the screen, with

00:24:58.106 --> 00:24:59.786 A:middle
this voice activation and speech

00:24:59.786 --> 00:25:00.166 A:middle
input.

00:25:00.786 --> 00:25:02.796 A:middle
It's hands-free and eyes free.

00:25:03.116 --> 00:25:04.926 A:middle
I can control my home, send

00:25:04.926 --> 00:25:06.526 A:middle
messages, and even start

00:25:06.526 --> 00:25:08.086 A:middle
workouts quickly with apps like

00:25:08.086 --> 00:25:08.516 A:middle
Zova.

00:25:09.656 --> 00:25:12.486 A:middle
And also, new this year is being

00:25:12.486 --> 00:25:14.336 A:middle
able to type to Siri that is

00:25:14.336 --> 00:25:16.246 A:middle
available in accessibility

00:25:16.246 --> 00:25:16.646 A:middle
settings.

00:25:17.106 --> 00:25:18.816 A:middle
This gives quick access to

00:25:18.816 --> 00:25:19.806 A:middle
someone who may not be able to

00:25:19.806 --> 00:25:20.316 A:middle
speak.

00:25:20.386 --> 00:25:21.896 A:middle
Or maybe you're just in a public

00:25:21.896 --> 00:25:22.336 A:middle
setting.

00:25:22.986 --> 00:25:26.716 A:middle
So, lastly, along with sight and

00:25:26.716 --> 00:25:28.156 A:middle
sound, is touch.

00:25:28.716 --> 00:25:31.026 A:middle
You can ask yourself, are your

00:25:31.026 --> 00:25:32.076 A:middle
apps tactile?

00:25:32.856 --> 00:25:34.366 A:middle
On supported devices adding

00:25:34.366 --> 00:25:36.126 A:middle
haptics provides a way to

00:25:36.206 --> 00:25:37.936 A:middle
physically engage people through

00:25:37.936 --> 00:25:38.456 A:middle
feel.

00:25:38.456 --> 00:25:41.036 A:middle
It gets your attention if sight

00:25:41.036 --> 00:25:42.366 A:middle
and sound are not an option.

00:25:42.716 --> 00:25:44.236 A:middle
But also, provides an

00:25:44.306 --> 00:25:45.676 A:middle
enhancement for everyone.

00:25:46.686 --> 00:25:48.876 A:middle
For example, some

00:25:48.876 --> 00:25:50.706 A:middle
system-provided interface

00:25:50.706 --> 00:25:52.056 A:middle
elements such as switches,

00:25:52.056 --> 00:25:54.036 A:middle
sliders, pickers, index

00:25:54.036 --> 00:25:55.936 A:middle
scrubbers provide haptic

00:25:55.936 --> 00:25:57.166 A:middle
feedback when we interact with

00:25:57.166 --> 00:25:59.196 A:middle
them to reinforce the action

00:25:59.356 --> 00:26:00.046 A:middle
that we're doing.

00:26:01.286 --> 00:26:06.726 A:middle
And a haptic on pull to refresh,

00:26:07.106 --> 00:26:08.316 A:middle
let's you know that you've

00:26:08.516 --> 00:26:10.356 A:middle
reached the critical threshold

00:26:10.626 --> 00:26:12.606 A:middle
between scrolling and refreshing

00:26:12.866 --> 00:26:14.256 A:middle
that shares a continuous

00:26:14.256 --> 00:26:14.736 A:middle
gesture.

00:26:16.086 --> 00:26:20.466 A:middle
And likewise, with swipe to

00:26:20.466 --> 00:26:20.916 A:middle
delete.

00:26:21.296 --> 00:26:22.856 A:middle
The haptic provides the critical

00:26:22.856 --> 00:26:24.876 A:middle
threshold of the accelerated

00:26:24.876 --> 00:26:27.076 A:middle
delete swipe.

00:26:27.546 --> 00:26:31.136 A:middle
And then another example is

00:26:31.136 --> 00:26:31.746 A:middle
Siri.

00:26:31.746 --> 00:26:34.356 A:middle
It uses a success haptic as a

00:26:34.356 --> 00:26:35.906 A:middle
confirmation that she heard what

00:26:35.906 --> 00:26:36.416 A:middle
you said.

00:26:42.726 --> 00:26:44.886 A:middle
Or Apple Pay uses visuals

00:26:44.886 --> 00:26:46.876 A:middle
haptics and sound with the

00:26:46.876 --> 00:26:49.756 A:middle
confirmation for the successful

00:26:49.756 --> 00:26:50.266 A:middle
purchase.

00:26:50.846 --> 00:26:52.406 A:middle
It feels the way it looks and

00:26:52.406 --> 00:26:53.716 A:middle
sounds, leaving me with a

00:26:53.716 --> 00:26:59.156 A:middle
confident purchase or payment

00:26:59.156 --> 00:26:59.223 A:middle
[ding].

00:26:59.223 --> 00:27:01.446 A:middle
Now, that's clear.

00:27:02.106 --> 00:27:04.706 A:middle
So, to see if your apps are

00:27:04.706 --> 00:27:07.236 A:middle
perceivable, ask yourself is it

00:27:07.236 --> 00:27:07.866 A:middle
legible?

00:27:08.336 --> 00:27:09.556 A:middle
Can I read it?

00:27:09.766 --> 00:27:10.696 A:middle
Is it audible?

00:27:10.696 --> 00:27:12.156 A:middle
Is it usable without site?

00:27:13.056 --> 00:27:14.096 A:middle
Is it tactile?

00:27:14.096 --> 00:27:14.946 A:middle
Can I feel it?

00:27:15.736 --> 00:27:17.386 A:middle
Take one away, or even two of

00:27:17.386 --> 00:27:20.646 A:middle
these can I still understand it.

