00:28:35.756 --> 00:28:37.766 A:middle
So, as our understanding of the

00:28:37.766 --> 00:28:40.086 A:middle
world has improved, so have our

00:28:40.826 --> 00:28:40.956 A:middle
maps.

00:28:43.436 --> 00:28:45.696 A:middle
Today, your map understands

00:28:45.696 --> 00:28:46.486 A:middle
where you are.

